    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/ywhwyf-mp/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=626145919695323699&sectionId=626145919728878131)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gguCnwVa854_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gguCnwVa854_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Frame_1484580952_80c40562-ca10-49d4-9ebc-102373a42a14.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUYRw8nmHu_text","label":"ggUYRw8nmHu_text","default":"How Thousands of Burned-Out Working Moms Are Getting Compliment-Worthy Skin Without the 10-Step Routine"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqhWzU5tdE_text","label":"ggqhWzU5tdE_text","default":"<p>No more layering. No more guesswork. Just real glow — fast.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggTy2IY0Ux_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gggTy2IY0Ux_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Group_37930_2_1_70c03fae-b732-46aa-bb33-b11ee550a6b8.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsdxtqBRbP_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggsdxtqBRbP_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/418ec590-74d5-413b-a8ee-0cf4f039fd0e.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","label":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","default":"<p><i>By Jane Miller | Updated: May 2025</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsWY_OmHqm_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggsWY_OmHqm_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Bio_Collagen_Main_Photo_2_22b3adc2-0470-49e4-9bff-94ea2a6c1c17.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1I25rv2az_text","label":"gg1I25rv2az_text","default":"<p>Most working women barely have time to finish their coffee, let alone commit to a complicated 10-step skincare routine. Between early mornings, late meetings, and back-to-back responsibilities — childcare, work deadlines, dinner prep, and more —&nbsp;<strong>skincare becomes just another item on an already overwhelming to-do list.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s no surprise that by the time most women hit their&nbsp;<strong>30s and 40s,</strong> their skin reflects the burnout: dullness, dryness, and that constant&nbsp;<strong>“perma-tired”</strong> look that even makeup can’t fully cover. Many have cycled through expensive creams, trendy TikTok serums, and influencer-recommended routines, only to feel frustrated by inconsistent results.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The truth? Aging skin — especially for women balancing real life — needs something different.&nbsp;<strong>Something smarter, simpler, and actually sustainable.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIh9jAl7hW_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggIh9jAl7hW_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_447778010_431048143184490_4824332307233201183_n_1080.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6uIDISuu8_text","label":"gg6uIDISuu8_text","default":"The Real Issue: Skincare Wasn’t Designed for Busy Women"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9mt8SYjhb_text","label":"gg9mt8SYjhb_text","default":"<p>The modern skincare world caters to trends, not to real people. Ten-step routines, 15-minute YouTube tutorials, $200 facials — <strong>these are luxuries that most busy women can't afford.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For women in their 30s, 40s, and beyond, the issue goes deeper. Dermatologists confirm that&nbsp;<strong>collagen production starts to decline after age 25,</strong> and hydration retention <strong>decreases steadily each decade.</strong> By the time many women are in their 40s, they’re dealing with more pronounced fine lines, uneven tone, and overall skin fatigue.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But here’s the thing: <strong>this doesn’t have to mean giving up on your skin. It just means choosing smarter tools</strong> — not more of them.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnKs4UR8Tl_label","label":"ggnKs4UR8Tl_label","default":"<p>GET YOURS NOW</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/image9.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Advertorial_Images_2f3da1d6-3f16-4da1-9f43-68e3973172bd.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/image9.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","label":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","default":"The Discovery: Nifora Mask"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvDN5djePx_text","label":"ggvDN5djePx_text","default":"<p>More and more women are discovering a one-step solution that fits into their real lives — and actually works.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It started in a quiet group chat among working moms. One woman posted a selfie, and the response was immediate: <strong>“What skincare are you using? You’re glowing!”</strong>&nbsp;Her answer?&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6elAxV66l_text","label":"gg6elAxV66l_text","default":"<p>The&nbsp;Nifora Bio-Collagen Mask — a once or twice a week ritual that’s become a skincare savior for women juggling it all.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Here’s what thousands of women report experiencing:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Day 1:</strong> Softer, smoother skin — like after a spa facial.<br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Day 3:</strong> A healthy glow begins to show up in natural light.<br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Day 5:</strong> The under-eyes appear brighter, more rested.<br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Day 7:</strong> Fine lines visibly soften. Skin looks firmer and makeup-free confidence returns.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And they keep using it — not out of obligation, but because the glow speaks for itself.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8P26fUryi_label","label":"gg8P26fUryi_label","default":"<p>GET YOURS NOW</p>"}],
